Package: leoclient2-leovirtstarter-client
Architecture: all
Suggests: 
Pre-Depends: leoclient2-leovirtstarter-common
Depends: libfilesys-df-perl, liblog-log4perl-perl, zenity
Description: alternativ software to start VirtualBox
 leovirtstarter2-client copies and caches VirtualBox snapshots and starts
 them


Package: leoclient2-leovirtstarter-server
Architecture: all
Suggests: 
Pre-Depends:
Depends: leoclient2-leovirtstarter-common
Description: prepare snapshots for leovirtstarter-client 
 leovirtstarter-server compresses snapshots and determines theis sizes and 
 syncs them to other servers


